@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_oobgue(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v0
    v2 = v1
    v2 = (v1 / ((tmp + 0.22 - v1 + 0.13) - (v0 + 0.31 - v1 + 0.37)))
    v1 = 0.95
    v0 = (wp.cos(v0) * wp.abs(wp.sin(v0 + 0.72)))
    tmp = wp.abs((wp.exp(tmp + 0.01) + (v0 + 0.55 * tmp + 0.20)))
    v1 = ((tmp - (tmp + 0.52 / v1 + 0.18)) - wp.sin(0.95))
    v0 = (wp.cos((v2 + 0.34 * tmp + 0.05)) / ((tmp + 0.07 + v2 + 0.28) * v0))
    data[tid] = v0
